<knimeNode icon="voronoi.png" type="Visualizer" xmlns="http://knime.org/node/v2.8" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://knime.org/node/v2.10 http://knime.org/node/v2.10.xsd">
    <name>Geo Map Viewer</name>
    
    <shortDescription>
        View a shapefile in a map
    </shortDescription>
    
    <fullDescription>
        <intro>
        This node writes out the input data table into an ESRI <a href="https://www.esri.com/library/whitepapers/pdfs/shapefile.pdf">shapefile</a>
        and then render the shapefile in a map view. The coordinate reference system for the map view is by default WGS84. 
        The input table must contain a geometry column ("the_geom") in GeoJSON format.         
		</intro>
                
